Below are lists of political parties espousing [[Islam]]ic identity or [[political Islam]] in various approaches under the system of [[Islamic democracy]]. Islamic democracy refers to a political ideology that seeks to apply Islamic principles to public policy within a democratic framework. Lists are categorized by the ideological affiliation and sorted by the country of origin.

